---
title: Pesto, Tomato & Cheddar Hasselback Chicken with Roast Potato & Broccoli
description: Hasselback chicken? You better believe it. This handy little trick is just the thing for adding flavour to an otherwise plain chicken breast. Plus, it stops the chicken from drying out. Fill the slices with basil pesto and top with fresh tomato and Cheddar cheese for an easy weeknight win.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5be2430930006c48e621e032-1551e0ca.jpg
